'''太空堡垒卡拉狄加：計畫'''（'''Battlestar Galactica: The Plan'''）是一部依据重拍版美国科幻电视剧[[太空堡垒卡拉狄加|太空堡垒卡拉狄加]]的故事人物设定而进行拍摄的电视电影。该片除了穿插在电视剧中播出的旧片段，同时还播出了很多新的故事情节，从而揭露了[[賽隆人|賽隆人]]的计划。

该片定于2009年10月27日推出DVD版本和蓝光版本，同时还提供影片下载服务。<ref name=prem>{{cite news |author= |url=http://sev.prnewswire.com/entertainment/20090717/LA4793117072009-1.html |title=From Universal Studios Home Entertainment: Experience the Fight for Humanity's Survival Through the Eyes of the Cylons for the First Time Ever In Battlestar Galactica: The Plan |date=2009-07-17 |work=[[PR_Newswire|PR Newswire]] |accessdate=2009-07-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091029160143/http://sev.prnewswire.com/entertainment/20090717/LA4793117072009-1.html |archivedate=2009-10-29 }}</ref> 并且暂定于2010年在[[Syfy|Syfy]]频道播出。<ref name=ct090915>{{cite news | author = Maureen Ryan | url = http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/entertainment_tv/2009/09/battlestar-galactica-plan.html | title = 'Plan' for 'Battlestar' fans: Wait a little longer for TV movie | date = 2009-03-17 | work = [[Chicago_Tribune|Chicago Tribune]] | accessdate = 2009-09-15 | archive-date = 2016-09-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160913230052/http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/entertainment_tv/2009/09/battlestar-galactica-plan.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>

